scene.message:
Maki: Wait!{nl}
That monster looks strong.{waitkey}{clearbox}Like Kurouri said,{nl}
let's try the shrine{nl}
maybe we'll learn something!{waitkey}{ret}

Demon: I am the gate and{nl}
the key... son of{nl}
Yog-Sothoth...{waitkey}{clearbox}To the unworthy,{nl}
the gate shall never open...{nl}
fu... fushuroo...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I won't eat fish{nl}
for a while... and it{nl}
reeks something awful.{waitkey}{clearbox}{ctl0f:1}, I hate to say it,{nl}
but as we are now,{nl}
we can't beat this thing.{waitkey}{clearbox}Like it or not, we'll have{nl}
to heed that shady{nl}
man's advice.{waitkey}{ret}

Yog-Sothoth Jr.:{nl}
One who bears the{nl}
Mirror of Harming...{waitkey}{clearbox}But unless you defeat me,{nl}
none shall pass.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Figured it'd come{nl}
to this!{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, let's go!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Leave this creature{nl}
be and it may grow{nl}
bigger than a stable.{waitkey}{nl}
Now's our only chance!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Are we really{nl}
fighting this thing?{waitkey}{nl}
Ayase can't say she{nl}
likes this look...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: This guy's got{nl}
no taste...{nl}
And he reeks of fish!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: No time to stand{nl}
around griping.{waitkey}{nl}
Don't beat this thing,{nl}
we don't reach him.{waitkey}{ret}
